---

>> source: Brian Lagerstrom

Add @Hot Sauce{300%g}, @Garlic Gloves{4}, @Worcestershire Sauce{20%g}, and @Distilled Vinegar{15%g} to sauce pan over medium high heat. Whisk ingredients together and allow to cook for ~{5%minutes} until thickened slightly. Whisk in the @Unsalted Butter{150%g}.